Subject: [PATCH] drm/xe: Fix early wedge on GuC load failure
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: a39d082c3553d35b4fe5585e1e2fb221c130cae8
